40 FOR X=0 TO 255 STEP 6
50 MOVE 128,96
60 DRAW X,0
70 NEXT X
80 FOR X=0 TO 255 STEP 6
90 MOVE 128,96
100 DRAW X,191
110 NEXT X
120 FOR Y=0 TO 191 STEP 6
